longBusinessSummary: Halcyon Agri Corporation Limited, an investment holding company, originates, produces, and distributes natural rubber products in Singapore, China, the United States, Canada, Europe, rest of Asia, and internationally. It operates through Corrie MacColl Group; HRC Group; and Corporate segments. The company processes and produces crumb rubber and latex, as well as constant viscosity rubber products; and owns rubber plantations land in Malaysia, Cameroon, and Ivory Coast. It provides its natural rubber primarily under the HeveaPRO brand. The company offers its products for use in tyres, shoe soles, medical gloves, seals, gaskets, and other applications through a network of logistics assets, storage and terminals, laboratories, and sales offices. It is also involved in trading and distribution of natural rubber, latex, and synthetic rubber; and manufactures and distributes plastic products. The company was founded in 1934 and is headquartered in Singapore. Halcyon Agri Corporation Limited is a subsidiary of China Rubber Investment Group Co., Ltd.
